366
00:28:39,039 --> 00:28:42,640
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je šest kuhinja, bilo je kuhinja za sve.

367
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi ljudi su kritizirali hranu.

368
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:48,799
